[
  {
    "startTime": 8.01,
    "endTime": 10.01,
    "text": "I'm scared, Professor Dumbledore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.28,
    "endTime": 14.799999999999999,
    "text": "Everyone is scared of something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Riddikulus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.73,
    "endTime": 20.240000000000002,
    "text": "Newt, you are next."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.32,
    "endTime": 28.25,
    "text": "That's an unusual one. What Mr. Scamander fears above everything else is..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.669,
    "endTime": 31.669,
    "text": "Having to work in an office, Sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.94,
    "endTime": 34.94,
    "text": "Go ahead, Newt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.69,
    "endTime": 38.69,
    "text": "Riddikulus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.39,
    "endTime": 49.39,
    "text": "Magic blooms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.379,
    "endTime": 53.379,
    "text": "Only in rare souls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.8,
    "endTime": 60.278999999999996,
    "text": "Still we must skulk  in shadows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.18,
    "endTime": 73.62,
    "text": "But the old ways serve us no longer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.62,
    "endTime": 86.14,
    "text": "Take it you've heard the rumors. Grindelwald had a vision that he  would rise to dominance over the Wizarding World."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.82,
    "endTime": 89.91999999999999,
    "text": "So you're asking me to help hunt him down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.92,
    "endTime": 98.24,
    "text": "I can't move against Grindelwald."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.12,
    "endTime": 100.76,
    "text": "It has to be you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.4,
    "endTime": 104.60000000000001,
    "text": "In your shoes, I'd probably refuse too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.84,
    "endTime": 106.84,
    "text": "It is late. Good evening Newt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.04,
    "endTime": 109.10000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.6,
    "endTime": 116.96,
    "text": "You underestimate your talents, Mr. Scamander."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.26,
    "endTime": 123.5,
    "text": "Their arrogance is the key to our victory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.02,
    "endTime": 131.02,
    "text": "Muggles are not lesser"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.59,
    "endTime": 137.59,
    "text": "not disposable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.78,
    "endTime": 144.1,
    "text": "You're too good, Newt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.48,
    "endTime": 147.48,
    "text": "You never met a monster you couldn't love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.86,
    "endTime": 150.70000000000002,
    "text": "Credence ?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.28,
    "endTime": 164.08,
    "text": "Mr. Scamander, do you think Dumbledore will mourn for you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.74,
    "endTime": 180.46,
    "text": "- Are you a ghost?  - No, I'm alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.74,
    "endTime": 183.92000000000002,
    "text": "Well, I'm an alchemist and therefore immortal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.92,
    "endTime": 184.42,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.42,
    "endTime": 186.33999999999997,
    "text": "Nicholas Flamel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.35,
    "endTime": 187.48999999999998,
    "text": "Jacob Kowalski."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.78,
    "endTime": 190.78,
    "text": "You don't look a day over 375."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.86,
    "endTime": 209.74,
    "text": "I have some questions for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.74,
    "endTime": 211.22,
    "text": "Professor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.24,
    "endTime": 213.64000000000001,
    "text": "This is a surprise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.22,
    "endTime": 217.26,
    "text": "There's a rumor that Newt Scamander is headed to Paris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.35,
    "endTime": 223.499,
    "text": "I know he's working under your orders."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.28,
    "endTime": 228.9,
    "text": "What do you have to say for yourself, Dumbledore?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.24,
    "endTime": 235.78,
    "text": "If you'd ever had the pleasure to teach him, you'd know Newt is not a great follower of orders."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.92,
    "endTime": 242.92,
    "text": "The time's coming, Newt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.23,
    "endTime": 248.23,
    "text": "When you're gonna have to pick a side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.52,
    "endTime": 252.84,
    "text": "Are you going somewhere?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.84,
    "endTime": 254.84,
    "text": "No. We're going somewhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.6,
    "endTime": 256.36,
    "text": "Genius!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.12,
    "endTime": 286.84000000000003,
    "text": "I can't move against Grindelwald."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.82,
    "endTime": 289.42,
    "text": "It has to be you."
  }
]